sections.heading: registry; hospital; failure to report; penalty
sections.text: Any hospital which fails to make reports as provided in sections 81-642 to 81-649.02 shall be guilty of a Class V misdemeanor for each offense.SourceLaws 1991, LB 703, ยง 76;Laws 2025, LB376, ยง 33.Effective Date: September 3, 2025
